{"tid":1692071,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"環球時報專訪伍淑清　斥青年人被洗腦　會放棄他們","createTime":"2019-11-04T02:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T02:41:29.000Z","uid":270703,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5bee4a5c9fd90664d4c363fc69c9b0e07985eb99","tid":1692071,"uid":270703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:18:18.000Z","msg":"老老實實，元氣門口仲係好多人排隊，爭氣啲得唔得，人地而家要放棄你地喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489919-20191104.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489919-20191104.htm&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfuoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=e1274048\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489919-20191104.htm&h=0c696549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489919-20191104.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n香港美心集團創辦人長女伍淑清接受內地《環球時報》專訪，批評特區政府部分公務員，為了保持所謂「政治中立」而無所作為，更有甚者認不清自己的身份去參加反政府遊行，她認為，特區政府應反思處理危機的能力和經驗。<br />\n<br />\n伍淑清又說，香港近期風波暴露出的另一大問題，是青年人的思想狀況。她指出，長年忽視對年輕人的國民教育，導致香港很多年輕人完全被社交媒體洗腦，成為反政府、反體制和反中國的人，這將是一個不容易解決的問題，她認為，社會已經失去整整兩代年輕人，而她會放棄這些年輕人，不會再浪費時間去跟他們講甚麼，因為他們的腦子已經不清楚自己應該做甚麼事情。她又相信，香港經濟的下行週期恐怕至少要持續三年。"},{"pid":"daf2f268e8002089a86cf4a30a9067e3ae739553","tid":1692071,"uid":147367,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:22:30.000Z","msg":"好好笑，一個就死既人話要放棄社會既未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e285eb07ad99e523caffcc2883e88662f6ba16bd","tid":1692071,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:23:15.000Z","msg":"直情同你有代溝喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係你放棄青年 係青年唔須理果頭近既你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d38d21493d666bde6db6704440286311828a11","tid":1692071,"uid":41116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:24:24.000Z","msg":"睇下你死先定我地死先"},{"pid":"cda705c7d462212d0fb81a81dfeb37e424d59f71","tid":1692071,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:25:53.000Z","msg":"豆腐婆"},{"pid":"7120cca4bb52dd2237dcf5f835f87d1b692a5cd8","tid":1692071,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:28:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf2b6d44d4ee0d87e75b9df4cf0759d528deed0a","tid":1692071,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:33:19.000Z","msg":"即係佢睇嘅媒體就係真，客觀，人地睇嘅就係假，洗腦"},{"pid":"bc19629ba47d9a36c4fbcd5623afc666c4b67717","tid":1692071,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:36:17.000Z","msg":"比甖骨灰放棄，好撚驚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b94f870944ad9c3e7242c6f605721fd61df6e7","tid":1692071,"uid":69761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:38:33.000Z","msg":"你快啲死算啦"},{"pid":"b853dbbc5f48e962e94a62611320065f0a2f9d3b","tid":1692071,"uid":248172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:39:33.000Z","msg":"睇來手足對美心太仁慈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fefb9357f3c5ed54d8e67282d3c2ce77ada451f","tid":1692071,"uid":245078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:39:47.000Z","msg":"其實係年輕人放棄左你條老野咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 